    {
      "name": "Countermeasure: Lumi's Battle Cry!",
      "description": "Adventure with Lumi! Depending on how you Tap, Lumi attacks in different forms.\n\nTap\nLumi strikes in a Super Power Form, attacking nearby enemies continuously, dealing AoE Geo DMG. If there are Moondrifts nearby, Lumi will also deal AoE Geo DMG to nearby enemies, which will be considered Lunar-Crystallize Reaction DMG.\n\nContinuous Tapping\nTime to show what we're really capable of! After using her Elemental Skill, Linnea will feed Lumi sparkling gemstones when her Elemental Skill or Normal Attack is Tapped repeatedly. A full-bellied Lumi will strike in her Ultimate Power Form, dealing an especially powerful instance of AoE Geo DMG that is considered Lunar-Crystallize Reaction DMG, switching to Standard Power Form.\nAdditionally, tapping the Elemental Skill increases Linnea's interruption resistance.\n\n\"You're up, Lumi!\"",
      "icon": "https://gi.yatta.moe/assets/UI/Skill_S_Linnea_01.png",
